Submitted files:
threadpool.c - implementaion of the threadpool.h file.
server.c - implementaion of http server the use threads pool method.

The program implements http server using threads pool method.
The program supports the functionality of sending files, dir content, handeling error : 302,400,403,404,500,501.
The server closes the connection with each client after his responde.
The number of client that the server can serve determinated at the args of the program (max-number-of-request).
Run the program useing the args: <port> <poolsize> <max-number-of-request>.
This program using threads - do not forget to use -pthread flag while compiling the program.
